-- Total Sells Stakes in Norwegian Valhall, Hod Fields to BP for $991 Million
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-04-27T06:04:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-27/total-sells-stakes-in-norwegian-valhall-hod-fields-to-bp-for-991-million.html

          
          
              Total SA said in an e-mailed
statement it sold its interests in the Valhall and Hod fields in
the Norwegian North Sea to BP Plc for $991 million.  
          
          


  


        